<RulesScreen>
    name: 'rules_screen'
    MDBoxLayout:
        orientation: 'vertical'
        MDLabel: 
            text: 'RULES:'
            halign: 'center'
            bold: True
            underline: True
            size_hint_y: .2
        ScrollView:
            background_color: 0, 0, 0, 0  # Make ScrollView background transparent
            BoxLayout:
                orientation: 'vertical'
                size_hint_y: None
                height: self.minimum_height
                MDLabel:
                    text: 
                        """When you do something risky, roll [b]1d6[/b]. Add [b]+1d6[/b] if you’re [b]prepared[/b] and [b]+1d6[/b] if you’re an [b]expert[/b].
                        \n\nRoll your dice and compare each die result to your stat [b]number[/b]:
                        \n\n 1. If you use [b]LASERS[/b], you succees by [b]rolling under[/b] your number.
                        \n - [b]LASERS[/b] is for science, reason, technology, cold rationality, and calm precise action.
                        \n\n 2. If you use [b]FEELINGS[/b], you succees by [b]rolling over[/b] your number.
                        \n - [b]FEELINGS[/b] is for rapport, diplomacy, intuition, seduction, and wild passionate action.
                        \n\n Success varies on number of dice that succeed:
                        \n 0. Fail
                        \n 1. Partial Success
                        \n 2. Success
                        \n 3. Critical Success! The GM tells you some extra effect you get.
                        \n\n [b]LASER FEELINGS[/b]
                        \n When you roll your number exactly, you have [b]LASER FEELINGS[/b]. The GM will tell you some incight into whats going on. 
                        \n - Ask the GM a question. They must answer you honestly.
                        \n - You can change your action if you want.
                        \n - then roll again.
                        \n\n [b]HELPING[/b]
                        \n If you want to help someone else who's rolling, say how you try to help and make a roll. If you succeed, give them +1d6 for that action.
                        """
                    markup: True
                    halign: 'center'
                    valign: 'middle'
                    size_hint_y: None
                    height: self.texture_size[1]
                    text_size: self.width, None
                    padding: dp(10), dp(10)
                    canvas.before:
                        Color:
                            rgba: 0, 0, 0, 0.75  # Ensure the label background is transparent
                        Rectangle:
                            pos: self.pos
                            size: self.size